<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Kc323vGBEqzTmouAECnVceyQqyqdsSiqLQISBL29aUW4U/M7pSPA/gEUZQqv1cwx4OnYxTxve5UMg5GT6L4JJg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

<style>
    .top-image {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 500px;
    }
    .top-img {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 80%;
        height: auto;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }
    .top-content {
        max-width: 1200px; /* Adjust max-width as needed */
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff; /* Example background color */
        color: #2f4507; /* Example text color */
    }

    .top-content h1, .top-content h2, .top-content h3 {
        color: #2f4507;
    }

    .top-content h1 {
        margin-bottom: 30px; /* Increase space below h1 */
    }

    .top-content h2 {
        margin-top: 30px; /* Increase space above h2 */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Adjust space below h2 if needed */
    }

    .top-content p, .top ul {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .top-content ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    /* Box Section */
    .boxes-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .box {
        flex: 1 1 calc(33.333% - 20px);
        margin: 10px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .box img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .box h3 {
        color: #2f4507;
        margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .read-more-btn {
        background-color: orange;
        border: none;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .read-more-btn:hover {
        background-color: blue;
    }

    .read-more-btn:active {
        background-color: blue;
    }
</style>

<!-- Image Section -->
<div class="top-image">
    <img src="/waste.png" alt="Mountain Image" class="top-img">
</div>

<div class="top-content">
    <h1>Sustainable Environment and Climate: Waste Management</h1>
    <p>
        At Mountain Forum Himalayas (MFH), we are dedicated to advancing effective waste management as a core element of environmental sustainability and climate change mitigation. Our strategy emphasizes minimizing waste generation through proactive measures like recycling, composting, and reducing reliance on single-use plastics. These efforts help conserve resources and reduce landfill dependency.
We implement comprehensive waste segregation and treatment systems to lower greenhouse gas emissions, particularly methane, a potent climate pollutant resulting from organic waste decomposition. Our sustainable waste management practices support the circular economy by transforming waste into valuable resources, such as energy or raw materials for new products.

    </p>
</div>



